          </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\" visible-xs\"><a href=\"../inquiry\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <div class=\"otoiawase-area\">\n          <p class=\"tel\"><img src=\"./images/common/ico_freedial.png\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" alt=\"フリーダイヤル\">0120-79-5520</p>\n          <p class=\"btn-inq\"><a href=\"../inquiry\">お問い合わせ</a></p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"tel visible-xs\"><img src=\"./images/common/ico_freedial.png\" width=\"21\" height=\"14\" alt=\"フリーダイヤル\"><a href=\"tel:0120795520\">0120-79-5520</a></p>\n  </header><!-- header-area-wrap-->\n  <div class=\"contents-area bg-inquiry\">\n    <h1 class=\"page-title\">お問い合わせ</h1>\n  </div>\n  <ul class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <li><a href=\"../\">ホーム</a></li>\n    <li>お問い合わせ</li>\n  </ul>\n  <div class=\"contents\">\n    <section class=\"service-block\">\n      <h2 class=\"title\">お問い合わせ窓口</h2>\n      <p class=\"tel-area\">ご質問・ご要望をお寄せください。</p>\n      <p class=\"tel-area freedial\"><img src=\"./images/common/fig_freesmp.png\" alt=\"\">0120-79-5520</p>\n    </section>\n    <section class=\"service-block\">\n          <h2 class=\"title\">メールでのお問い合わせ</h2>\n      <p class=\"mb20\">まことに勝手ながら、回答が遅くなることやメール以外の方法にて御連絡する場合がありますので、ご了承下さい。<br>\n                      またご内容によりお答えしかねることもございますので、あらかじめご了承下さい。<br>\n                      発明内容を詳細に書かれますと新規性を失う可能性がございますので、ぜひともご注意をお願い致します。</p>\n        <form id=\"form1\" name=\"form1\" method=\"post\">\n        <table class=\"tbl-border-rows inq\">\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>お問い合わせ先</th>\n            <td>\n              <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"inq\" value=\"1\" />住宅</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"inq\" value=\"2\" />リクルート</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"inq\" value=\"3\" />その他</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>お名前</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" class=\"w-name\" maxlength=\"40\" value=\"\" />\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>フリガナ</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"kana\" class=\"w-kana\" maxlength=\"40\" value=\"\" />\n             \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th>会社名（学校名）</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"school\" class=\"w-school\" maxlength=\"40\" value=\"\" />\n             \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th>郵便番号</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"zip\" class=\"w-zip\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" />\n             \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th>住所</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"address\" class=\"w-address\" size=\"50\" maxlength=\"200\" value=\"\" />\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>電話</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"tel\" class=\"w-tel\" maxlength=\"13\" value=\"\" />\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th>fax</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"fax\" class=\"w-fax\" maxlength=\"13\" value=\"\" />\n             \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>メールアドレス</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"mail\" class=\"w-mail\" maxlength=\"100\" value=\"\" />\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>メールアドレス（確認）</th>\n            <td>\n              <input type=\"text\" name=\"cmail\" class=\"w-mail\" maxlength=\"100\" value=\"\" />\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <th><p class=\"label hissu\">必須</p>お問い合わせ内容</th>\n            <td>\n              <textarea name=\"contents\" cols=\"40\" rows=\"6\" class=\"w-contents\"></textarea>\n              \n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n        <p class=\" text-center mb20\" >お客様の個人情報の取り扱いにつきましては、<a href=\"../privacy/\">「個人情報保護方針（プライバシーポリシー）」</a>をご確認ください。</p>\n        <p class=\" text-center\" ><input type=\"submit\" value=\"確認する\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-large center-block\" /></p>\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"action\" value=\"check\" />\n      </form>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n\n  <footer class=\"footer\">\n    <div class=\"page-top\">\n      <span><a class=\"scroll\" href=\"#page-top\">▲</a></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"footer-in clearfix\">\n      <div class=\"clearfix\">\n        <div class=\"footer-main\">\n          <p class=\"footer-logo\"><a href=\"../\"><img src=\"./images/common/logo_footer.png\" alt=\"チューモク株式会社\"></a></p>\n          <address>本社　〒939-1704 富山県南砺市田中793　TEL 0763-52-2808　FAX 0763-52-6366</address>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer-secondary\">\n          <ul class=\"footer-nav list-unstyled list-inline\">\n            <li><a href=\"../privacy\">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <small class=\"copyright\">Copyright &copy; CHUMOKU CO.All rights reserved.</small>\n    </div>\n  </footer></body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"https://www.chumoku.co.jp/inquiry/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T21:14:34.311Z"}